{"tid":628441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首登艦觀演 蔡英文：非與習對抗 專家：兩岸皆出精銳 中國大陸壓倒性優勢","createTime":"2018-04-14T00:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T14:29:10.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"91ed1971490aa053b6ab607a05294c7f182dca66","tid":628441,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T00:46:27.000Z","msg":"首登艦觀演 蔡英文：非與習對抗 專家：兩岸皆出精銳 陸壓倒性優勢<br />\n是深具信心」。<br />\n<br />\n黃東：台剩美國牌可出<br />\n<br />\n澳門國際軍事學會會長黃東對本報，兩岸都拿出最好的東西，明顯今時今日台灣同大陸「無得比」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180414/s00013/1523643263636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180414%2Fs00013%2F1523643263636&d=W7b%2BWNj1u%2BV7aCy48ljdW%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=74678b87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180414%2Fs00013%2F1523643263636&h=104d3402\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180414/s00013/1523643263636</a>"},{"pid":"9456662b4844ccfb97aba476d4ce67835bae5b50","tid":628441,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T00:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96f597ffc429bb5238f6eaa88050efee3e9b082","tid":628441,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":36,"score":-35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T00:56:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ca9e085b2c95058256df1c4e4a74819f834c867","tid":628441,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T00:59:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca0301e39cd51523b89162d5b99bd2b822c012c3","tid":628441,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T01:04:47.000Z","msg":"[red]澳門國際軍事學會會長黃東［/red]對本報，兩岸都拿出最好的東西，明顯今時今日台灣同大陸「無得比」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同支那人無分別，日日打飛機！"},{"pid":"38ea45c58a1e47383355dda99823b542f6748b99","tid":